1
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:39,400
[Royal Feast]

2
00:01:41,190 --> 00:01:43,620
[Episode 35]

3
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:45,760
It's tasty

4
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,080
but too hot.

5
00:01:56,639 --> 00:01:57,160
Your Majesty,

6
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:58,680
I'll stand guard outside.

7
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:00,760
Directress Su,

8
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,879
your dishes are delicate.

9
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:04,680
Officer You

10
00:02:04,919 --> 00:02:06,559
can't wait to go out for some pancakes.

11
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,960
Nice. It's delicious.

12
00:02:22,119 --> 00:02:22,839
Coming. Coming.

13
00:03:09,399 --> 00:03:10,039
Directress Yin.

14
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,399
Although you can change
the order of serving food,

15
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:15,119
you still must observe
the principle of going from salty to mild

16
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,759
and from thick to thin.

17
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,039
By messing up the order,

18
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,720
you spoil the appetite

19
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:21,440
and the original taste of the food.

20
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:27,199
What is this?

21
00:03:27,399 --> 00:03:29,240
I have never seen it before.

22
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:30,600
Your Highness,

23
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,800
this is a rice roll.

24
00:03:33,279 --> 00:03:35,039
The filling is crunchy and delicious

25
00:03:35,279 --> 00:03:37,240
even though it is just
pickled vegetables and eggplants.

26
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,639
It's yummy!

27
00:03:40,650 --> 00:03:42,080
[Rice Roll]

28
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,520
Big Brother, try it too.

29
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,240
I think you are hungry.

30
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,600
Where is this dish from?

31
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:49,600
Your Majesty.

32
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,440
It is said that when the Yuan Dynasty's army

33
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,279
retreated from Nan'an Prefecture in Jiangxi,

34
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,160
the food in the city was looted.

35
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,919
A quick-witted and nimble-fingered woman

36
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:58,679
collected broken rice

37
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,000
on the ground

38
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,839
and ground it into a gruel.

39
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:02,600
She steamed it in a winnowing basket

40
00:04:02,679 --> 00:04:04,119
and used all kinds of fillings.

41
00:04:04,119 --> 00:04:05,559
Then she brushed tea-seed oil

42
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,960
to make very delicious rice rolls.

43
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,839
It is super delicious.

44
00:04:10,039 --> 00:04:11,440
It doesn't look special,

45
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:13,000
but it's very fragrant.

46
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:19,875
[Crab Roe Soup Dumpling]

47
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:23,359
Your Highness.

48
00:04:23,799 --> 00:04:24,839
Don't eat so fast even if you're hungry.

49
00:04:25,839 --> 00:04:27,200
The soup dumpling doesn't look hot,

50
00:04:28,119 --> 00:04:28,839
but if you're not careful,

51
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,679
you can have heartburn.

52
00:04:32,359 --> 00:04:33,519
You are right, Officer You.

53
00:04:34,239 --> 00:04:35,640
It is said that during the Three Kingdoms period,

54
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,399
Sun Quan married off his sister to Liu Bei.

55
00:04:37,959 --> 00:04:39,519
Madam Sun had loved to eat crabs since young.

56
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,720
Away from her native place,

57
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,799
she missed crabs even more.

58
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,760
Then, someone used crab roe as the filling

59
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:44,600
for soup dumplings

60
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,760
in memory of her.

61
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:47,320
It's hot,

62
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,720
but it should be eaten hot.

63
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,839
It has a crab smell when it cools down.

64
00:04:54,119 --> 00:04:56,200
Stuffed Rice Rolls accompanied by
Crispy Juntun Stuffed Flatbread.

65
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,880
This flatbread

66
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:58,760
was a military ration handed down

67
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,480
by General Jiang Wei

68
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,959
from the Three Kingdoms period.

69
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,040
Officer You, please try it.

70
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,359
I forgot to remind you

71
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,799
that there's pepper powder inside.

72
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:24,040
You better try the fried cake first

73
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,040
or sugar rolls.

74
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,559
Officer You,

75
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,119
are you alright?

76
00:05:31,119 --> 00:05:32,519
Do I look alright?

77
00:05:33,559 --> 00:05:34,359
Sir, forgive me.

78
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:36,279
I ground the pepper myself

79
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,279
and the taste is heavier.

80
00:05:37,679 --> 00:05:39,160
Did you give me

81
00:05:39,679 --> 00:05:40,720
a pot of pepper powder?

82
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:46,040
Yunzhou often leaves Beijing for assignments.

83
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,880
You must have tasted food

84
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:48,799
from all localities.

85
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:49,880
How could there

86
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,079
be something you haven't tasted?

87
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,200
All the cuisines of the world converge in China.

88
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:54,720
If one eats three meals

89
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,320
of fresh delicacies every day

90
00:05:56,679 --> 00:05:57,600
and lives to be 1,000 years old,

91
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,959
he still can't finish sampling the delicacies.

92
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,880
This is Sheep Head Meat Roll.

93
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,119
Wang Anshi, counselor-in-chief
of the Song Dynasty,

94
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,040
considered fame and wealth as floating clouds.

95
00:06:16,399 --> 00:06:17,880
When he studied late at night,

96
00:06:18,119 --> 00:06:19,519
he loved this Sheep's Head Meat Roll.

97
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,920
In Wang's Residence,

98
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,040
the best Sheep Head Meat Roll

99
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,920
was not made by the cook of the residence

100
00:06:25,119 --> 00:06:26,399
or Madam Wang,

101
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,679
but...

102
00:06:27,679 --> 00:06:28,279
Who?

103
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:31,519
This is a long story.

104
00:06:57,359 --> 00:06:58,160
Noble Consort Sun,

105
00:06:59,239 --> 00:07:01,399
I like Directress Yin's stories.

106
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,640
Let her cook for me in the future.

107
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:07,880
Your Majesty,

108
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:10,679
you took Directress Su personally,

109
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:14,160
now you want to take Directress Yin too.

110
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,160
What if I'm not used to

111
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,519
the meals made by others?

112
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,880
What should I do?

113
00:07:20,119 --> 00:07:20,880
I will exchange with you.

114
00:07:23,559 --> 00:07:24,600
This...

115
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,040
I'm afraid that's not good.

116
00:07:28,799 --> 00:07:29,760
If Her Majesty likes it,

117
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:31,799
let Directress Yin

118
00:07:32,279 --> 00:07:33,679
prepare meals for Kunning Palace in the future.

119
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,720
Thank you, Your Majesty.

120
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,279
Yes, Your Majesty.

121
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,160
We can't wait any longer.

122
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,679
Now is the best time.

123
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:06,440
Wait.

124
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:12,000
Leave me.

125
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:23,279
They are prepared.

126
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:24,480
Retreat.

127
00:08:25,119 --> 00:08:25,679
Let's go.

128
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,000
Eunuch Chen, you did not stand guard
outside the shack

129
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,880
to serve His Majesty.

130
00:08:30,559 --> 00:08:31,399
Where did you go?

131
00:08:31,679 --> 00:08:33,000
Directress Yin has to prepare food.

132
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,719
So, I walked around.

133
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,400
Walked around?

134
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:49,840
I have to change my clothes. Do as you please.

135
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,359
Forgive me, Brother.

136
00:08:56,479 --> 00:08:57,840
I did not do it on purpose.

137
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,000
With you as my brother,

138
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,760
I would have more grey hair.

139
00:09:01,239 --> 00:09:02,679
I'll check if the soup is ready.

140
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:10,320
I'll see how Directress Yin

141
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,400
cook.

142
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,000
Your Majesty, please go ahead.

143
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:31,239
Your Highness is generous.

144
00:09:31,719 --> 00:09:32,880
You even gave away your chef.

145
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:34,599
As far as I know,

146
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:36,280
Directress Yin is illiterate.

147
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,320
Even after studying for two years,

148
00:09:39,239 --> 00:09:40,280
she still cannot talk about cuisines

149
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:41,840
with great familiarity.

150
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,080
Who do you think

151
00:09:43,719 --> 00:09:45,080
was the storyteller?

152
00:09:46,599 --> 00:09:47,479
How dare you question me

153
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:50,080
just because you won His Majesty's favor?

154
00:09:50,599 --> 00:09:51,919
You've overstepped.

155
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,239
How many of Chen Wu's subordinates

156
00:09:54,239 --> 00:09:55,400
are office workers from the Eastern Depot?

157
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,559
He won't even dare unveil some things.

158
00:09:57,559 --> 00:09:58,599
Naturally, there are reasons for that.

159
00:10:00,679 --> 00:10:01,719
After today,

160
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,559
the eunuchs and officials involved

161
00:10:03,559 --> 00:10:04,599
will hate you down to the bone.

162
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:07,000
You don't even care about your reputation.

163
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:08,200
I am

164
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:10,359
short-sighted.

165
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:13,640
I only care about the present.

166
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:15,400
I can't control the future.

167
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:20,440
What can't you control?

168
00:10:22,599 --> 00:10:23,200
Your Majesty.

169
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:27,840
I only like

170
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:30,159
this flatbread with rice noodles.

171
00:10:30,799 --> 00:10:31,679
I'll eat as I please.

172
00:10:32,359 --> 00:10:33,159
I already approved.

173
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:34,239
No one can tell you what to do.

174
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,599
That was more

175
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:43,919
or less what happened.

176
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:48,479
Your Majesty,

177
00:10:49,159 --> 00:10:50,640
permit me to speak out of turn.

178
00:10:51,359 --> 00:10:52,559
Noble Consort Sun

179
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:54,159
is out of control

180
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:56,119
because His Majesty likes her.

181
00:10:57,719 --> 00:10:58,400
According to old rules,

182
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:00,039
Her Majesty

183
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,320
should be bestowed a gold sculpture
and gold foil edict.

184
00:11:01,799 --> 00:11:03,080
While the Noble Consort is only given
the gold foil edict.

185
00:11:04,239 --> 00:11:06,520
However, His Majesty bestowed upon
the Noble Consort a gold sculpture also.

186
00:11:06,919 --> 00:11:07,799
This

187
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,840
has never happened in all dynasties.

188
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:10,679
Moreover, it should be the only honor

189
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:11,760
in the land under heaven.

190
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:13,559
He also said

191
00:11:14,119 --> 00:11:15,119
that if you didn't stop it,

192
00:11:15,599 --> 00:11:16,880
a big mistake would have been committed.

193
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,559
Therefore,

194
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:19,840
you are wise.

195
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,640
You saw through that with one glance.

196
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:25,599
Sha Soup is here.

197
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:26,799
What soup?
(*"sha" can mean "what")

198
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,039
Yes. Sha Soup.

199
00:11:34,664 --> 00:11:36,025
[Sha Soup]

200
00:11:41,359 --> 00:11:42,159
Didn't His Majesty

201
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:43,840
insist on giving Noble Consort Sun

202
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,039
a gold sculpture?

203
00:11:47,359 --> 00:11:48,119
Tell him

204
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:49,840
I approve of it.

205
00:11:55,253 --> 00:11:58,050
[Foods Office]

206
00:12:22,817 --> 00:12:24,800
[Radish Pastry]

207
00:12:26,245 --> 00:12:27,875
[Steamed Sponge Cake]

208
00:12:56,545 --> 00:12:58,650
[Tanghulu]

209
00:13:30,237 --> 00:13:31,700
[The Sixth Month of the First Year
of the Xuande Reign]

210
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:47,479
Stop.

211
00:13:50,799 --> 00:13:52,320
I taught you when you first entered the palace

212
00:13:52,719 --> 00:13:53,880
about which bowls or plates

213
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:55,440
to use for different food.

214
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:56,679
Even the best food

215
00:13:56,679 --> 00:13:57,960
must be matched with beautiful implements.

216
00:13:58,599 --> 00:13:59,239
Are you dumb

217
00:13:59,239 --> 00:14:00,239
or deaf?

218
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:04,960
How could you cry

219
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,440
when you've done something wrong?

220
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:06,960
Kneel.

221
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:13,760
Greetings, Your Majesty.

222
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:16,679
Come here and sit.

223
00:15:20,599 --> 00:15:21,880
Your Majesty, don't you know

224
00:15:22,119 --> 00:15:23,640
that Directress Yin is a close friend
of Noble Consort Sun?

225
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:25,039
Don't invite a wolf into your house.

226
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:26,200
I know.

227
00:15:26,919 --> 00:15:28,280
If you know, Your Majesty,

228
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:29,679
why do you trust this person?

229
00:15:31,039 --> 00:15:32,520
Directress Yin came to cook for me

230
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,039
with the approval

231
00:15:34,039 --> 00:15:34,960
of His Majesty.

232
00:15:35,880 --> 00:15:36,520
Moreover,

233
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:38,440
meals delivered to Kunning Palace

234
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:40,159
are carefully checked and tested.

235
00:15:40,679 --> 00:15:41,479
I'm not afraid.

236
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:42,760
What are you worried about?

237
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:44,719
Noble Consort Sun has ulterior motives.

238
00:15:44,719 --> 00:15:45,919
She wins people over easily.

239
00:15:46,359 --> 00:15:46,760
Your Majesty,

240
00:15:46,760 --> 00:15:47,760
don't be bewitched by her

241
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:49,039
and court disaster.

242
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:50,200
Moreover,

243
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:51,960
the Imperial Food Service has many cooks.

244
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,640
[Fried Sangza]
Directress Yin's culinary skills may not be...

245
00:15:54,359 --> 00:15:56,200
It's fragrant and crispy.

246
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:56,840
Try it.

247
00:16:07,039 --> 00:16:08,719
Although Directress Yin started
as a palace maid,

248
00:16:09,239 --> 00:16:10,159
she knows a lot

249
00:16:10,159 --> 00:16:11,039
about the stories of food.

250
00:16:12,039 --> 00:16:13,280
That was a nice story.

251
00:16:13,599 --> 00:16:14,479
Tomorrow, I will come and listen.

252
00:16:22,039 --> 00:16:22,520
Sir,

253
00:16:23,520 --> 00:16:24,719
His Majesty suddenly summoned us
to accompany him.

254
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:25,960
Be careful.

255
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:26,960
What is there to watch out for?

256
00:16:27,159 --> 00:16:28,440
What are you saying?

257
00:16:28,520 --> 00:16:29,119
Sir,

258
00:16:29,880 --> 00:16:31,039
after His Majesty returned to the palace
from paying homage at the mausoleum,

259
00:16:31,039 --> 00:16:32,440
he severely punished all officials involved.

260
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,119
The Wardens' Offices of the Five Wards
and the Ward-Inspecting Censors

261
00:16:34,119 --> 00:16:35,159
were severely reprimanded.

262
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:36,679
What if His Majesty takes his anger on you?

263
00:16:36,919 --> 00:16:37,440
Sir.

264
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,039
Officer You,

265
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:43,000
it's time to set off.

266
00:16:43,679 --> 00:16:44,359
Eunuch Chen,

267
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:46,039
where are we going to?

268
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:47,280
I'll tell you on the way.

269
00:16:48,520 --> 00:16:49,239
Let me drive the carriage.

270
00:17:44,760 --> 00:17:45,400
It's this path.

271
00:17:46,439 --> 00:17:47,119
To play it safe,

272
00:17:47,280 --> 00:17:48,160
place two people on each path

273
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:48,839
and track them.

274
00:17:49,199 --> 00:17:50,280
Report immediately if you get any news.

275
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:51,160
Yes.

276
00:17:51,280 --> 00:17:52,040
You, come with me.

277
00:17:52,359 --> 00:17:52,760
Yes.

278
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:41,640
Eunuch Chen,

279
00:18:42,119 --> 00:18:42,680
your people from the Eastern Depot

280
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:43,760
are getting more and more capable.

281
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:46,040
Officer You, what do you mean?

282
00:18:46,959 --> 00:18:48,199
The imperial bodyguard
came along to escort His Majesty,

283
00:18:48,479 --> 00:18:50,000
but the sun is high and they're not here yet.

284
00:18:50,520 --> 00:18:51,599
