00:36:10,399 --> 00:36:12,560
I heard that Xi Shi loved to pick lotus for food

577
00:36:12,560 --> 00:36:14,600
to nourish her extraordinary beauty.

578
00:36:14,919 --> 00:36:16,239
That was why the later generations claimed

579
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:17,879
the lotus could clear the heat
and cool the blood.

580
00:36:18,120 --> 00:36:19,600
It is also beauty food.

581
00:36:22,080 --> 00:36:22,719
Porridge

582
00:36:22,719 --> 00:36:24,560
served with fried salted shredded fish

583
00:36:24,560 --> 00:36:25,159
[Fried Salted Shredded Fish]
tastes the best.

584
00:36:26,120 --> 00:36:27,560
Didn't you say it was hot yesterday?

585
00:36:27,840 --> 00:36:29,719
Today, I specially prepared Ice with Cream.

586
00:36:30,159 --> 00:36:32,159
[Ice with Cream]
However, Your Majesty has just resumed eating

587
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:33,239
and shouldn't eat too much,

588
00:36:33,879 --> 00:36:34,919
or it might be bad for your body.

589
00:36:38,239 --> 00:36:39,159
Your Majesty,

590
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:41,719
I don't know what I did wrong

591
00:36:42,399 --> 00:36:44,239
to displease you.

592
00:36:46,679 --> 00:36:47,199
Your Majesty.

593
00:36:47,199 --> 00:36:48,159
Noble Consort Sun

594
00:36:48,159 --> 00:36:49,239
is waiting outside the hall as summoned.

595
00:36:49,879 --> 00:36:50,719
Let her in.

596
00:36:51,040 --> 00:36:51,560
Yes.

597
00:37:02,239 --> 00:37:04,120
Greetings, Your Majesty.

598
00:37:11,639 --> 00:37:12,719
I didn't serve a good meal.

599
00:37:12,959 --> 00:37:14,120
Please forgive me.

600
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:14,760
No need.

601
00:37:15,959 --> 00:37:16,679
Noble Consort Sun,

602
00:37:17,479 --> 00:37:18,520
take her back.

603
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:20,919
I don't want to see her again.

604
00:37:23,439 --> 00:37:24,239
Your Majesty.

605
00:37:24,239 --> 00:37:24,919
Directress Yin.

606
00:37:25,399 --> 00:37:26,639
I have something to say to Her Majesty.

607
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:27,719
Please leave us.

608
00:37:46,959 --> 00:37:48,159
Your Majesty hates me

609
00:37:49,239 --> 00:37:50,439
because of Matron Hu?

610
00:37:54,719 --> 00:37:55,639
Noble Consort Sun,

611
00:37:57,159 --> 00:37:58,919
I know His Majesty favors you very much,

612
00:37:59,959 --> 00:38:01,520
but I am the Empress.

613
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:04,320
You are going too far.

614
00:38:05,199 --> 00:38:06,520
I did not explain earlier

615
00:38:07,959 --> 00:38:09,560
because it is obvious.

616
00:38:10,879 --> 00:38:12,159
With your wisdom,

617
00:38:12,560 --> 00:38:14,120
how could you misunderstand?

618
00:38:14,919 --> 00:38:15,800
Unless

619
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:17,159
you

620
00:38:17,159 --> 00:38:19,600
are venting your displeasure
and anger over the loss of a loved one

621
00:38:20,120 --> 00:38:21,439
on me.

622
00:38:23,959 --> 00:38:26,399
(I sincerely pray to heaven)

623
00:38:27,199 --> 00:38:28,879
(that you may live in peace and joy.)

624
00:38:29,560 --> 00:38:30,560
(This wish is enough.)

625
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:36,040
Had you not entered the palace,

626
00:38:38,679 --> 00:38:40,280
and without you in the world...

627
00:38:40,879 --> 00:38:41,719
Your Majesty.

628
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:43,120
You lost your sister,

629
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:45,040
but what about me?

630
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:47,479
You took the Empress' position.

631
00:38:48,159 --> 00:38:50,719
I do not have any foothold in this world.

632
00:38:51,159 --> 00:38:51,919
In this world,

633
00:38:52,040 --> 00:38:53,479
there is no one to protect me.

634
00:38:54,439 --> 00:38:55,520
Have you ever thought

635
00:38:56,479 --> 00:38:57,479
of my past situation?

636
00:38:58,199 --> 00:38:59,719
Everything is predestined.

637
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:02,439
Can people

638
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:05,239
deny their fate?

639
00:39:06,199 --> 00:39:07,080
Look at me.

640
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:10,040
Was my fate cast in stone?

641
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:14,320
Life is full of twists and turns

642
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,040
and unpredictable.

643
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:17,879
Why must you accept your fate?

644
00:39:18,719 --> 00:39:19,600
What were you thinking

645
00:39:20,600 --> 00:39:21,800
over half a year?

646
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:27,000
Water.

647
00:39:27,879 --> 00:39:29,360
Water benefits many but takes no credit.

648
00:39:30,520 --> 00:39:31,800
Even in the most painful situation,

649
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:33,600
I will tell myself

650
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:35,959
that if there are boulders ahead,

651
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:38,000
I will take a detour.

652
00:39:39,439 --> 00:39:40,760
What if there is no detour?

653
00:39:41,399 --> 00:39:42,520
If I can't detour,

654
00:39:43,159 --> 00:39:44,879
the constant dripping of water
will make a hole in the boulders.

655
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:49,080
His Majesty went on tour in plain clothes

656
00:39:49,199 --> 00:39:50,320
and returned after 7 PM.

657
00:39:51,439 --> 00:39:53,600
He finished reviewing memorials
on the fourth watch.

658
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:56,280
He did it because he wished to be

659
00:39:56,280 --> 00:39:57,320
an enlightened ruler.

660
00:39:58,320 --> 00:39:59,959
However, people concealed
the true states of affairs from all

661
00:39:59,959 --> 00:40:00,919
and confused the public.

662
00:40:01,439 --> 00:40:02,800
He has to personally see,

663
00:40:02,800 --> 00:40:03,959
listen, and visit.

664
00:40:05,439 --> 00:40:06,800
Even the soles of his boots were torn.

665
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:09,959
The son of heaven doesn't always get his wish.

666
00:40:10,199 --> 00:40:11,679
What more can ordinary people expect?

667
00:40:12,600 --> 00:40:13,399
Your Majesty,

668
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:16,479
please reinvigorate yourself

669
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:18,560
and continue living properly.

670
00:40:48,959 --> 00:40:49,639
Your Majesty,

671
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:50,959
the food is cold.

672
00:41:31,719 --> 00:41:33,600
She clearly gave the instruction
not to deliver meals anymore,

673
00:41:33,600 --> 00:41:34,840
but she changed her mind in an instant.

674
00:41:35,040 --> 00:41:35,439
How did you

675
00:41:35,439 --> 00:41:37,000
persuade Her Majesty?

676
00:41:39,239 --> 00:41:41,159
The weather is hot
and there are many government affairs.

677
00:41:42,239 --> 00:41:43,639
Naturally, His Majesty
has intense internal heat.

678
00:41:43,639 --> 00:41:44,560
He is more irritable.

679
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:45,879
You should cook more

680
00:41:45,879 --> 00:41:47,639
food that clears heat and dryness.

681
00:41:48,439 --> 00:41:50,080
I checked all the menus you sent me.

682
00:41:50,719 --> 00:41:52,719
Several dishes have scallion
and peppers in them.

683
00:41:52,719 --> 00:41:54,120
You should remove such food

684
00:41:54,439 --> 00:41:55,159
that promotes dryness.

685
00:41:57,959 --> 00:41:59,000
Why are you so quiet

686
00:41:59,000 --> 00:42:00,080
and why stare at me?

687
00:42:00,399 --> 00:42:01,040
Yes.

688
00:42:01,199 --> 00:42:02,040
I'll change that.

689
00:42:14,360 --> 00:42:15,120
I'll go back.

690
00:42:16,560 --> 00:42:18,239
You're so meticulous

691
00:42:18,239 --> 00:42:19,280
about His Majesty's diet and daily life.

692
00:42:19,719 --> 00:42:21,199
However, others are still criticizing you
behind your back.

693
00:42:21,199 --> 00:42:22,439
They say that you are cunning,

694
00:42:22,439 --> 00:42:23,479
good at winning people over,

695
00:42:23,919 --> 00:42:24,679
and you wrap His Majesty

696
00:42:24,679 --> 00:42:26,239
around your little finger.

697
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:27,560
According to you,

698
00:42:28,159 --> 00:42:28,879
given his temperament,

699
00:42:28,879 --> 00:42:30,280
can His majesty be easily manipulated?

700
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:34,800
You should

701
00:42:35,719 --> 00:42:37,159
deliver the meal a bit later.

702
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:40,000
Let them talk first.

703
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:43,320
I'm leaving.

704
00:43:00,159 --> 00:43:01,080
Do you have a son?

705
00:43:04,239 --> 00:43:05,879
I ask you if you have a son?

706
00:43:06,399 --> 00:43:08,600
I have two sons.

707
00:43:09,879 --> 00:43:10,760
You have two sons

708
00:43:11,840 --> 00:43:12,239
but didn't

709
00:43:12,239 --> 00:43:13,800
send them to learn craftsmanship.

710
00:43:13,800 --> 00:43:14,679
Your Majesty, I...

711
00:43:14,719 --> 00:43:15,280
You were short of craftsmen

712
00:43:15,280 --> 00:43:16,679
and stopped projects that weren't urgent.

713
00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:20,000
Why did you go to Yingtian Prefecture

714
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:22,040
to choose 5,000 children
to come to Beijing to learn craftsmanship?

715
00:43:23,080 --> 00:43:24,520
You are a father.

716
00:43:24,879 --> 00:43:26,080
Don't you feel compassion and sympathy

717
00:43:26,080 --> 00:43:27,199
for their parents?

718
00:43:27,719 --> 00:43:28,439
Your Majesty.

719
00:43:28,919 --> 00:43:29,439
This...

720
00:43:30,080 --> 00:43:31,959
This is the arrangement
of the Directorate of Palace Eunuchs.

721
00:43:32,479 --> 00:43:34,520
I'm telling the truth.

722
00:43:35,719 --> 00:43:36,800
Telling the truth?

723
00:43:38,600 --> 00:43:39,959
As the Minister of Works,

724
00:43:40,919 --> 00:43:42,040
you didn't listen and report

725
00:43:42,919 --> 00:43:44,080
when you should have.

726
00:43:44,760 --> 00:43:45,320
Get out.

727
00:43:56,360 --> 00:43:57,840
Aren't you in charge
of the Directorate of Palace Eunuchs?

728
00:43:59,639 --> 00:44:00,159
Your Majesty,

729
00:44:00,879 --> 00:44:01,760
I have no idea about that.

730
00:44:02,080 --> 00:44:03,479
I don't know, Your Majesty.

731
00:44:04,159 --> 00:44:04,800
It wasn't me.

732
00:44:05,199 --> 00:44:06,280
Your Majesty, Your Majesty.

733
00:44:06,439 --> 00:44:07,639
I'm innocent.
